{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-101-whats-new-in-cocoa"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"The Cocoa frameworks give you high-level access to the underlying power of Mac OS X. Get a developer’s eye overview of the Lion advances in Foundation and Application Kit, including support for new features such as Full-screen, Auto Save, Resume, Versions, and many others. This session will orient you for the other Cocoa sessions that cover these technologies in further detail.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"title":"What’s New in Cocoa","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading":"WWDC11","role":"sampleCode"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"article","sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/101\/","overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","isActive":true},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-101-Whats-New-in-Cocoa"},"references":{"WWDC11-Icon.png":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-Icon.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"WWDC11-Icon.png","alt":null,"type":"image"},"WWDCNotes.png":{"type":"image","alt":null,"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"u